{"tid":585182,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個最討厭嘅教學方式","createTime":"2018-03-08T12:12:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T14:37:03.000Z","uid":167389,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"28db1e010ed45ac5502ecc3a02e9df0f53c54238","tid":585182,"uid":167389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T12:12:55.000Z","msg":"每個人係求學時段都應該遇過啲濕鳩老師，通常啲老師濕鳩都係因為佢地啲教學方式。<br />\n<br />\n我先：<br />\n個老師係教心理學嘅堂，但堂堂淨係講佢係外國留學啲經歷，講到自己有幾威識幾多人（例如佢個朋友拉小提琴有幾勁）但完全同課程內容無關嘅。之後又針對我地果班，我地果班講少少中文比人鬧成堂，佢教其他班就無鬧過。<br />\n<br />\n平時呢個課程avg一定係A/A+但我地果班全班最高B+<br />\n<br />\n最後佢仲要鬧我地欺負一個平時上堂都煩9住我地嘅煩膠。<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家有無啲咁嘅濕鳩老師教書嘅經歷呢"},{"pid":"318ae948e530df957692b80a61bc97b516ebbc45","tid":585182,"uid":163974,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T12:16:55.000Z","msg":"欺你老母負<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82615c782f4dda3ee8a1ea524597a0bf40972bd7","tid":585182,"uid":140580,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T12:18:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"992ac32fa83ed62437fcfaedcd2171c1f01e8ffd","tid":585182,"uid":137233,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T12:19:27.000Z","msg":"所有九點堂"},{"pid":"7030c670b328114a1adf981709f33f73b58ce502","tid":585182,"uid":136467,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T12:22:56.000Z","msg":"俾爛grade 嘅prof<br />\n講一套做一套個d prof<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9a25b650a3e80b9112608ccd89c4b594d869daa","tid":585182,"uid":105911,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T13:48:55.000Z","msg":"唔同嘅教學方式都有人彈：<br />\n跟住課本教就話照書讀，講下題外話又話你吹水，分組活動就話dum波鐘，究竟有冇啲係大家都覺得好嘅教學方法？"},{"pid":"73aefa1c5ab2fb1c61ef48df07fecbb1ac2f97c9","tid":585182,"uid":73910,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e9a25b650a3e80b9112608ccd89c4b594d869daa","tid":585182,"uid":105911,